    "extract": "Piyush Gupta is a Singaporean banker and the chief executive officer (CEO) of DBS Group between 2009 and 2025. He is vice-chairman of the Institute of International Finance since 2013, and a board member of Enterprise Singapore since 2024.",
    "extract_html": "<p><b>Piyush Gupta</b> is a Singaporean banker and the chief executive officer (CEO) of DBS Group between 2009 and 2025. He is vice-chairman of the Institute of International Finance since 2013, and a board member of Enterprise Singapore since 2024.</p>"
